                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130602-82-off434 t18130602-82-cd435"></join>, a handkerchief, value 4 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18130602-82-victim779" type="victimName">
                           John Charles 
